<div class="app-card-container">
  <div class="card">
    <h1>About Me</h1>
    <hr>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-5">
        <%= image_tag "https://static.pexels.com/photos/69372/pexels-photo-69372.jpeg", width: 300, alt: "Profile Image", class: 'profile-img' %>
        <div class="skills">
          <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
            <div class="skill">
              <h4><%= skill.title %></h4>
              <div class="progress">
                <div
                  class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-warning"
                  role="progressbar"
                  aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utilized %>"
                  aria-valuemax="100"
                  style="width: <%= skill.percent_utilized %>%"
                > </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-md-7">
         <p> I am 13 years old, <!--<em>but my mental age could be slightly lower. </em>-->
          am currently majoring in absolutely nothing and have no idea where I'm heading with my life.
         I have a family, which consists of me, my mom, my dad, and my younger sister. I'm currently trying to add a new addition to the family-
         a dog- but my mom won't let me :( Another problem would be the fact that I'm allergic to dogs and other things,
         but that's not going to stop me from getting one! </p>
       
         <p> Another fact you might want to know about me is that I am <em> really</em> short, or at least for my age.
         I'm not even five foot yet, so that's pretty sad. I blame genetics.</p>
         
         <p> 
           <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#jobHistory"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controler="jobHistory"
           >
           Job History
           </button> 
           
            <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#education"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controler="education"
           >
            Education
          </button> 
        </p>
        
        <p>
          <div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
            <div class="card card-block">
              Job 1
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              Job 2
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="collapse" id="education">
            <div class="card card-block">
              School 1
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              School 2
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              School 3
            </div>
          </div>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
